{"tid":1061603,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到完場系列] 老公侍產全紀錄 續集","createTime":"2019-03-14T13:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T09:38:20.000Z","uid":10901,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b395ffee30b250c7de3da2fa969ae857d862761","tid":1061603,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"上集喺高登<br />\n<br />\n[推到完場系列] 老公侍產全紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6540287&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6540287%26page%3D1&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=7e032e5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6540287&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n續集<br />\n話説預產期係今個月廿幾號<br />\n老婆零晨三點開始痛<br />\n我同呀仔就繼續瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到七點頂唔順<br />\n八點去醫院 留院<br />\n十二點幾我就去返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準時收工就仆去醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過咗七點半就返屋企沖涼食麵再返醫院standby<br />\n食食吓麵老婆打嚟話: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好痛呀！</strong></span></span><br />\n如是者飛的又到醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家同幾個 準/現役 爸爸坐喺產前病房等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUtdnMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUtdnMM.png&h=5910cac8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bacfc15bf5fa40e6c2e855dc74037f1c7d1fafa","tid":1061603,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"老婆打嚟嗌好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410e4f032c